<chapter><title>Button Classes</title>
<indexterm><primary>Classes</primary>
<secondary>Buttons</secondary></indexterm>

<para>Buttons are widgets that when clicked cause an event to be signaled. There are a
number of different button types and classes including push buttons, check boxes,
radio buttons, spin buttons, and others.</para>

